genresAdvancedInfo.name: ambient fusion
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Ambient fusion is a genre that combines elements of ambient music with other genres such as jazz, world music, and electronic music. It creates a unique sound that is often characterized by its use of live instruments and intricate melodies. This genre is perfect for those who want to relax and unwind while listening to music that is both soothing and engaging.
